Every time someone hits a shot from a certain distance, they get a reward.
30-50 blocks    - 1 iron
50-100 blocks   - 1 iron and 1 gold
100-200 blocks  - 1 iron, 1 gold and 1 diamond
200+ blocks     - 2 iron, 3 gold and 5 diamonds

Commands:
Operators only:
/longshots enable/on/true/start   - Enables the scenario
/longshots disable/off/false/stop - Disables the scenario
